---
title: Carb Smart Loaded Bunless Turkey Burgers with Arugula and Spinach
description: Any night can be burger night, sometimes we just leave the bun behind! Start with a nutritious salad base then add the juicy all-turkey patties and pile on the tasty toppings real high.

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
